Package org.jlab.coda.hipo

Enum Class HeaderType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<HeaderType>
org.jlab.coda.hipo.HeaderType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<HeaderType>, Constable
public enum HeaderType extends Enum<HeaderType>
Numerical values associated with types of record headers, file headers and trailers. The value associated with each enum member is stored in the header's bit-info word in the top 4 bits.
Since:
6.0 9/6/17
Version:
6.0
Author:
timmer
